quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,"Noon, Kasam hai qalam ki aur us cheez ki jisey likhne waley likh rahey hain"
  68,2,Tum apne Rubb ke fazl se majnoon (deewane) nahin ho
  68,3,Aur yaqeenan tumhare liye aisa ajar (reward) hai jiska silsila kabhi khatm honay wala nahin
  68,4,Aur beshak tum akhlaaq ke bade martabe par ho
  68,5,Anqareeb tum bhi dekh logey aur woh bhi dekh lenge
  68,6,Ke tum mein se kaun junoon (madness) mein mubtala hai
  68,7,"Tumhara Rubb un logon ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo uski raah se bhatkey huey hain , aur wahi unko bhi acchi tarah jaanta hai jo raah-e-raast par hai"
  68,8,Lihaza tum in jhutlane walon ke dabao mein hargiz na aao
  68,9,yeh to chahte hain ke kuch tum mudahnat (narmi) karo to yeh bhi mudahnat (narmi) karein
  68,10,Hargiz na dabo kisi aisey shaks se jo bahut kasmein khane wala be-waqaat (worthless) aadmi hai
  68,11,"Taaney deta hai , chugliyan khata phirta hai (slanderer, gossip-monger)"
  68,12,"Bhalayi se rokta hai , zulm-o-zyadti mein hadd se guzar janey wala hai, sakht badh-amal hai , jafa-kaar hai"
  68,13,Aur in sab uyub (aib) ke saath badh-asl (illegitimate child) hai
  68,14,Is bina par ke woh bahut maal-o-aulad rakhta hai
  68,15,Jab hamari aayat usko sunayi jati hai to kehta hai yeh to agle waqton ke afsane hain
  68,16,Ankareeb hum iski sund (snout) par daag lagayenge
  68,17,"Humne in (ehle makkah) ko usi taraah aazmaish mein dala hai jis tarah ek baagh (garden) ke maalikon ko aazmaish mein dala tha, jab unhon ne kasam khayi ke subah sawerey zaroor apne baagh ke phal todenge"
  68,18,Aur woh koi istasna (exception) nahin kar rahey thay
  68,19,Raat ko woh soye padey thay ke tumhare Rubb ki taraf se ek balaa is baagh par phir gayi
  68,20,Aur uska haal aisa ho gaya jaise kati hui fasal ho
  68,21,Subah un logon ne ek dusre ko pukara
  68,22,Kaha agar phal todne hai ho to sawerey sawerey apni kheti ki taraf nikal chalo
  68,23,Chunanchey woh chal padey aur aapas mein chupke chupke kehte jatay thay
  68,24,Ke aaj koi miskeen tumhare paas baag mein na aane paye
  68,25,Woh kuch na dene ka faisla kiye huye subah sawerey jaldi jaldi is tarah wahan gaye jaise ke woh (phal todne par) qadir hain
  68,26,Magar jab baagh ko dekha to kehne lagey “hum raasta bhool gaye hain
  68,27,Nahin balke hum mehroom reh gaye”
  68,28,Un mein jo sab se behtar aadmi tha usne kaha “maine tumse kaha na tha ke tum tasbeeh kyun nahin karte?”
  68,29,"Woh pukar utthey paak hai hamara Rubb, waqayi hum gunahgaar thay"
  68,30,Phir unmein se har ek dusre ko malamat karne laga
  68,31,"Akhir ko unhon ne kaha “afsos hamare haal par, beshak hum sarkash ho gaye thay"
  68,32,"Baeed (door) nahin ke hamara Rubb humein badle mein issey behtar baagh ata farmaye, hum apne Rubb ki taraf rujoo karte hain"
  68,33,"Aisa hota hai azaab aur aakhirat ka azaab issey bhi bada hai, kaash yeh log isko jaante"